{"title":"生命——献给英雄的歌","authors":["张胜友"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给英雄的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张胜友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命如此灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于春晓和煦的暖风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于夏夜绚丽的流星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于秋日金黄的谷穗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于冬季洁白的瑞雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命如此壮阔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于五岳高昂的头颅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于大海澎湃的涛声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于原野袒露的胸怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于蓝天翻飞的流云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命如此悠远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于江河万古长流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于花木常谢常开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于日月轮回有序"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于星辰辉耀长空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，生命如此美丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于珍视生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于保卫生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在于奉献生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的使者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高扬起世道人心……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}